title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft updates - Famous Flyer 7 and Expert series 1
description:
Last week the first update was released for two aircrafts the Famous Flyer 7: Mitsubishi Heavy Industries MU-2  and a mega update for the Expert Series 1: ATR 42-600 / 72-600.
In this video we will go through the release notes to see what has changed. And what is actually really cool is that the ATR also received some new functionality.
